<!-- EDIT2 SECTION "See also:" [32-93] -->
<h2 class="sectionedit3"><a name="frames" id="frames">frames</a></h2>
<div class="level2">
<pre class="code">frames()</pre>

<p>
Returns the number of <span class="curid"><a href="doku.php?id=main:modding_docs:lua:spriteset#frames" class="wikilink1" title="main:modding_docs:lua:spriteset">frames</a></span> in this sprite set.
</p>

</div>
<!-- EDIT3 SECTION "frames" [94-197] -->
<h2 class="sectionedit4"><a name="render" id="render">render</a></h2>
<div class="level2">
<pre class="code">render(bitmap, frame, x, y)</pre>

<p>
Draws the frame <em>frame</em> of the sprite set on <em>bitmap</em> with the pivot at position (x, y).
</p>

</div>
<!-- EDIT4 SECTION "render" [198-343] -->
<h2 class="sectionedit5"><a name="render_skinned_box" id="render_skinned_box">render_skinned_box</a></h2>
<div class="level2">
<pre class="code">render_skinned_box(bitmap, x1, y1, x2, y2, color)</pre>

<p>
Draws the sprite set as a skinned box with the rectangle (x1, y1) - (x2, y2)
and background color <em>color</em>.
</p>

<p>
<strong>Note that in versions before 0.9c, color was specified as
three parameters. This has been deprecated.</strong>
</p>

</div>
